Description: Create publication-ready timeline charts with 'ggplot2'.
    Supports multiple visual styles, elbowed connectors, automatic
    above/below label placement with staggered heights to reduce overlap,
    and full aesthetic mapping including grouping by shared colours and
    shapes.
URL: https://github.com/brooksbenard/ggtimeline
